---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Northville Tech"
  description="Who writes Northville Tech, why we exist, and how we make money."
>
  <div class="container-prose" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <h1>About Northville Tech</h1>
    <p class="small">Last updated April 2026.</p>

    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>
      Northville Tech reviews adventure experiences, gift-worthy activities, and the gear around them.
      We started as a YouTube channel in 2021 covering tech, and expanded into experience reviews because
      most of the "top 10 bucket list experiences" articles online are written by people who've never
      actually tried any of them. We have.
    </p>

    <h2>Our review standards</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We pay for the experience ourselves, or disclose clearly when we don't.</li>
      <li>We try it at least once before reviewing. Most flagship reviews are after 2+ sessions.</li>
      <li>We quote real prices, real wait times, and real trade-offs.</li>
      <li>We say when something is not worth it, because a review that never criticizes is a brochure.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we make money</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate commissions. When you click an affiliate link and book or buy, we earn a small percentage
      from the merchant — at no extra cost to you. That's the entire business model.
    </p>
    <p>
      We will never recommend something we don't believe in just because the commission is higher.
      If we wouldn't pay for it ourselves, it doesn't get recommended here. See the full{' '}
      <a href="/disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for specifics.
    </p>

    <h2>Who writes this</h2>
    <p>
      Northville Tech is run by a small team based in Michigan. We also run the{' '}
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@northvilletech" rel="noopener">@northvilletech YouTube channel</a>{' '}
      and an experience-focused short-form account. Questions, corrections, or story ideas? Reach us at{' '}
      <a href="mailto:hello@northvilletech.com">hello@northvilletech.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial independence</h2>
    <p>
      No brand pays us for coverage. No merchant sees our reviews before they publish. If an affiliate
      program tries to condition commissions on edits, we refuse and disclose the attempt.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
